couldn't manufacture an immunity?

57:36.707 --> 57:38.792
Look, DNA samples from the mother and baby
will tell us this.

57:39.168 --> 57:40.002
I'll set it up.

57:41.420 --> 57:44.089
Guys, no mention of her parents.

57:51.221 --> 57:51.847
Sorry, about that.

57:52.681 --> 57:54.141
Yeah, look, are you going to call
my fiancÃ©?

57:54.641 --> 57:58.061
Yes, but before we do that,
those men I was just speaking with,

57:58.687 --> 57:59.730
