- No, not that I know of.

01:02:39.468 --> 01:02:41.261
Those are two different answers.

01:02:44.973 --> 01:02:48.727
Do either of you have any religious
affiliations? Christian, Muslim?

01:02:49.311 --> 01:02:51.855
